"gnome-system-monitor და libgtop, clutter and Network Manager gir "
"bindings \n"
"\t    Debian-ზე და Ubuntu-ზე: gir1.2-gtop-2.0, gir1.2-nm-1.0, gir1.2-"
"clutter-1.0, gnome-system-monitor \n"
"\t    Fedora-ზე: libgtop2-devel, NetworkManager-libnm-devel, gnome-system-"
"monitor \n"
"\t    Arch-ზე: libgtop, networkmanager, gnome-system-monitor\n"
"\t    openSUSE-ზე: typelib-1_0-GTop-2_0, typelib-1_0-NetworkManager-1_0, "
"gnome-system-monitor \n"
"\t    64 ბიტიან Mageia-ზე: lib64gtop-gir2.0, lib64nm-gir1.0, lib64clutter-"
"gir1.0, gnome-system-monitor\n"

